{"image_id": "NFLX_2015_page_71", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "(“CODM”) reviews the operating results in assessing performance and allocating resources. The Company’s", "bbox": [143.8, 140.4, 1094.1, 161.2]}, {"text": "CODM reviews revenue and contribution profit (loss) for each of the reportable segments. Contribution profit", "bbox": [143.8, 165.4, 1094.0, 186.2]}, {"text": "(loss) is defined as revenues less cost of revenues and marketing expenses incurred by the segment. The", "bbox": [143.8, 190.4, 1094.2, 211.3]}, {"text": "Company has aggregated the results of the International operating segments into one reportable segment because", "bbox": [143.8, 215.4, 1094.1, 236.3]}, {"text": "these operating segments share similar long-term economic and other qualitative characteristics.", "bbox": [143.8, 240.4, 947.1, 261.3]}, {"text": "The Domestic streaming segment derives revenues from monthly membership fees for services consisting", "bbox": [185.5, 288.0, 1094.0, 308.9]}, {"text": "solely of streaming content to the members in the United States. The International streaming segment derives", "bbox": [143.8, 313.1, 1094.1, 333.9]}, {"text": "revenues from monthly membership fees for services consisting solely of streaming content to members outside", "bbox": [143.8, 338.1, 1094.1, 358.9]}, {"text": "of the United States. The Domestic DVD segment derives revenues from monthly membership fees for services", "bbox": [143.8, 363.1, 1094.0, 383.9]}, {"text": "consisting solely of DVD-by-mail. Revenues and the related payment card fees are attributed to the operating", "bbox": [143.8, 388.1, 1094.0, 408.9]}, {"text": "segment based on the nature of the underlying membership (streaming or DVD) and the geographic region from", "bbox": [143.8, 413.1, 1094.1, 433.9]}, {"text": "which the membership originates. There are no internal revenue transactions between the Company’s segments.", "bbox": [143.8, 438.1, 1077.8, 458.9]}, {"text": "The majority of cost of revenues relate to content expenses directly incurred by the segment. However, in", "bbox": [185.5, 485.7, 1094.2, 506.6]}, {"text": "connection with global expansion, content acquired, licensed, and produced increasingly includes global rights.", "bbox": [143.8, 510.7, 1094.1, 531.6]}, {"text": "The Company allocates this content between the International and Domestic streaming segments based on", "bbox": [143.8, 535.7, 1094.2, 556.6]}, {"text": "estimated fair market value. Other costs of revenues such as delivery costs are primarily attributed to the", "bbox": [143.8, 560.7, 1094.1, 581.6]}, {"text": "operating segment based on amounts directly incurred by the segment. Marketing expenses consist primarily of", "bbox": [143.8, 585.7, 1094.2, 606.6]}, {"text": "advertising expenses and payments made to our affiliates and device partners which are generally included in the", "bbox": [143.8, 610.7, 1094.1, 631.6]}, {"text": "segment in which the expenditures are directly incurred.", "bbox": [143.8, 635.8, 613.4, 656.6]}, {"text": "The Company’s long-lived tangible assets were located as follows:", "bbox": [185.5, 683.4, 744.3, 704.2]}, {"text": "As of December 31,", "bbox": [889.7, 725.7, 1027.7, 742.3]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [887.3, 750.7, 920.7, 767.4]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [996.8, 750.7, 1030.1, 767.4]}, {"text": "(in thousands)", "bbox": [908.1, 775.7, 1009.5, 792.4]}, {"text": "United States . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [185.5, 797.7, 833.7, 818.5]}, {"text": "$159,566", "bbox": [864.9, 797.7, 943.1, 818.5]}, {"text": "$138,704", "bbox": [974.4, 797.7, 1052.5, 818.5]}, {"text": "International . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [185.5, 822.7, 833.7, 843.5]}, {"text": "13,846", "bbox": [885.8, 822.7, 943.1, 843.5]}, {"text": "11,171", "bbox": [995.2, 822.7, 1052.5, 843.5]}, {"text": "The following